languages.text: "Отставить. Перестань позориться перед Лорд-капитаном. Я сама возглавлю допросы, если это лучшее, чего ты добился".
"Enough! You will not embarrass yourself in front of the Lord Captain any further. Since this is the best you've managed to do, I will take charge of the interrogations myself."

languages.text: « Assez ! Vous vous êtes suffisamment ridiculisé devant {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine}. Puisque vous n'êtes qu'un misérable incompétent, c'est moi qui vais me charger des interrogatoires. »
languages.original_text: "Enough! You will not embarrass yourself in front of the Lord Captain any further. Since this is the best you've managed to do, I will take charge of the interrogations myself."

languages.text: «¡Basta! No dejaré que te pongas en evidencia más delante de{mf|l| la} Lord Capitán. Si esto es lo mejor que has podido hacer, asumiré el control de los interrogatorios yo misma».
languages.original_text: "Enough! You will not embarrass yourself in front of the Lord Captain any further. Since this is the best you've managed to do, I will take charge of the interrogations myself."

languages.text: “够了！你不用继续在舰长大人面前出丑了。既然你只有这样的能耐，后面的审讯工作我准备亲自负责。”
languages.original_text: "Enough! You will not embarrass yourself in front of the Lord Captain any further. Since this is the best you've managed to do, I will take charge of the interrogations myself."

languages.text: 「十分だ！ロード・キャプテンの前で恥かくようなマネはするな。お前にとってはこれで精一杯だろうから、尋問は私が担当する」
languages.original_text: "Enough! You will not embarrass yourself in front of the Lord Captain any further. Since this is the best you've managed to do, I will take charge of the interrogations myself."
